reviewText: Ok to watch when there is nothing else to watch.

Awesome movie!  Simply the best!  Krista Allen is so sexy and beautiful.  If you are a Krista Allen fan, this movie will be an addition to your collection.  Recommendation:  A+++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Title says it all, if you are a fan of Krista Allen, then these are a must have.
It has a sense of humor, plenty of nudity and an imaginative storyline! What more can you ask from soft porn?
Almost a complete waste of time, no on second thought it is a complete waste of time.
